<normalizedToken originalValue="Elazığ">Elazig</normalizedToken>
from East Anatolia, where it grows on steppe between 1100- 
<pageBreakToken pageId="4" pageNumber="87" start="start">1200</pageBreakToken>
m of elevation. Species associated with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Eksi, Koyuncu &amp; Oezkan" authorityYear="2016" class="Liliopsida" family="Alliaceae" genus="Allium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Allium ekimianum" order="Asparagales" pageId="4" pageNumber="87" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ekimianum">
